Required softwares
------------------

* Markdown (The package name in Debian is "markdown".)
* xsltproc (The package name in Debian is "xsltproc".)

What should be done in the release process
------------------------------------------

* translating the lead paragraph
* adding, translating, and marking up the top title
* adding the footer section
  * including acknowledgment to all reviewers who gave comments
* unifying terminology
* squashing typos
  * checking spelling of personal names for typos
* checking for filtered characters such as mail addresses
* improving line break points for appearance
* inserting/deleting space characters for appearance
* making sure that all reference links included in the original text exists
* making the text as a correct Markdown document
